          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Ship it because any statistically significant lift is enough."
        },
        {
          "feedback": "A longer run may reduce uncertainty, but it will not turn a tiny effect into a useful one unless the effect estimate changes.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Keep running until the lift reaches the original target."
        },
        {
          "feedback": "The result is not proof of harm to the primary metric, but the costs and guardrails make the decision unattractive.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "text": "Call it a failed test because trial starts went down."
